entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You convinced Kaiya Merel, a Meatlump lieutenant, that two rogue CorSec officers with whom you were to meet were killed by CorSec agents. She seemed impressed that you escaped.
entries.journal_entry_description: Vani Korr has asked you to find a way into the Meatlump Hideout. First, you must find out where it is. To that end, you are trying to gain the confidence of a Meatlump lieutenant to infiltrate their ranks.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Kaiya Merel wants you to work with a couple of Rogue CorSec officers with whom she has been trying to establish a connection and help them highjack and destroy a shuttle. You are actually going to take out the two Rogue CorSec officers, Berinn Ebonette and Bechdo Ervekk, and then tell Kaiya that the meet with them was raided by CorSec agents.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Meet with the Rogue CorSec Officers
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Return to Kaiya Merel. Tell her that the two rogue CorSec officers were killed when CorSec agents raided your meet with them.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Defeat Bechdo Ervekk, a rogue CorSec officer.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Defeat Brrinn Ebonette, a rogue CorSec officer.
